The reimbursements mailbox poll job can't authenticate against Microsoft Graph.

Detail: <%= @detail %>

Most likely the Entra client secret has expired or been revoked. Receipt emails are
NOT being processed until this is fixed (they stay unread and will be picked up once
authentication works again).

Rotate the secret: entra.microsoft.com -> App registrations ->
"BlackLightning Reimbursements Mailbox" -> Certificates & secrets, then update the
Rails production credentials and redeploy.

This alert is sent at most once per day.
